ς\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al3-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>υἱὸς \u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"ΠριμιγένεωςΠριμιγνίτως\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"patronym\" data-text=\"ΠριμιγένεωςΠριμιγνίτως\">Πριμιγνίτως\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al4-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>μνήμης χάριν \u003Cbr id=\"al5-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">5\u003C/span>ἐποίησαν \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">l.1 reg., orig. ΙΧΝΔΤΙἸχνδτι | l.3 reg., orig. ΠΡΙΜΙΓΝΙΤΩΣΠριμιγνίτως\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>ΣΥΝΒΙ[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">···\u003C/span>]ΚΑΙΜΑΤΡΙ\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"ἸχνατίαἸχνδτι\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"ἸχνατίαἸχνδτι\">ΙΧΝΔΤΙ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ζαχαρίας\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ζαχαρίας\">ΖΑΧΑΡΙΑΣ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">···\u003C/span>]ΚΑΙ\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Κούϊντος\n                    υἱὸς ΠριμιγένεωςΠριμιγνίτως\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Κούϊντος\">ΚΟΥΙΝΤΟΣ\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al3-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>ΥΙΟΣ\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"ΠριμιγένεωςΠριμιγνίτως\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"patronym\" data-text=\"ΠριμιγένεωςΠριμιγνίτως\">ΠΡΙΜΙΓΝΙΤΩΣ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al4-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>ΜΝΗΜΗΣΧΑΡΙΝ\u003Cbr id=\"al5-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">5\u003C/span>ΕΠΟΙΗΣΑΝ\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">l.1 reg., orig. ΙΧΝΔΤΙἸχνδτι | l.3 reg., orig. ΠΡΙΜΙΓΝΙΤΩΣΠριμιγνίτως\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"facsimile-images\">\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic003556_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic003556_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic003556.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic003556-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"apparatus\">\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>\u003Cspan>Text after Kaibel and Filippi, with suggested restorations of SEG, prioritising Kaibel's transcription of the manuscript tradition.\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2> translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">  \u003C/p>\u003Cp>  \u003C/p>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"commentary\">\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>As Korhonen lucidly details, the inscription is one of a series of late 18th century local antiquarian forgeries, constructed on the basis of existing texts, principally those to be found in the 1769 first edition of the corpus of Torremuzza. Kaibel classed the entire series already as forgeries in IG XIV.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"bibliography\">\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> 52.0901 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig100007