 found in the 1769 first edition of the corpus of Torremuzza. Kaibel classed the entire series already as forgeries in IG XIV.\u003C/p>  ",{"id":258,"html":259},"bibliography","\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> 52.0901 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Kaibel 1890 \u003Ca href=\"https://clio.columbia.edu/catalog/6873760\" target=\"_blank\">22*\u003C/a>  \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Filippi 2002 75 no.7/3 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001991\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001991\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Filippi 2005 65 no.7/3 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002296\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002296\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Korhonen 2017 198 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001484\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001484\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  ",{"id":261,"html":262},"handnote"," Line 1    Interlineation line 1 to 2    ",{"id":264,"html":265},"license"," Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. ",[267,269,272,273],{"html":268},"Text encoding: Jonathan Prag",{"id":270,"lang":123,"html":271},"edition-interpretive","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>συνβί[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">...\u003C/span>] καὶ ματρὶ \u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"ἸχνατίαἸχνδτι\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"ἸχνατίαἸχνδτι\">Ἰχνδτι\u003C/span>\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpr